you know.

06:14.500 --> 06:15.918
AIDEN:
Is everything okay?

06:16.002 --> 06:19.380
SELVA:
Yeah, Celine's on the phone
with her sister in California.

06:19.463 --> 06:23.008
They're planning a hen party
or a baby shower

06:23.092 --> 06:24.968
or a presidential
inauguration ball.

06:26.720 --> 06:28.472
