and I don't want to know

06:28.555 --> 06:30.975
until it's all over.

06:34.062 --> 06:35.897
Here.

06:35.980 --> 06:37.690
Thanks.

06:45.155 --> 06:47.283
Well.

06:47.367 --> 06:48.450
Everything alright?

06:48.533 --> 06:50.285
Magazine? School?

06:50.368 --> 06:53.622
Yeah, everything's fine.

06:53.705 --> 06:55.248
Good.

06:57.960 --> 07:00.713
You look like you
need a break.

07:00.797 --> 07:02.382
Oh, really?

07:02.465 --> 07:03.590
Yeah, you do.

07:07.470 --> 07:08.387
SELVA:
Hey.

07:08.470 --> 07:10.598
Why don't we go out
this weekend.

07:10.682 --> 07:13.517
Go out to the bar,
have a few drinks, relax.

07:13.600 --> 07:15.562
I can watch you pick up
some chicks.

07:15.645 --> 07:17.230
Hey, I could be your...

07:17.313 --> 07:17.980
...wingman!

07:19.482 --> 07:22.443
Bruh, I don't need a wingman.

07:22.527 --> 07:27.573
Uh yeah, you do, bruh!

07:35.748 --> 07:37.833
You're late again.

07:37.917 --> 07:41.420
I know, sorry.

07:41.503 --> 07:43.755
