08:00.898 --> 08:03.233
Well, you know the real scoop
on everything

08:03.317 --> 08:05.318
that goes on around here, no?

08:06.278 --> 08:07.780
Don't believe everything
you hear.

08:07.863 --> 08:09.782
So they weren't going out

08:09.865 --> 08:12.827
or you don't know everything
that goes on around here?

08:20.752 --> 08:22.420
What is going on in here!

08:22.503 --> 08:23.837
Oh, my God, you are bleeding!

08:25.130 --> 08:27.173
That looks like it might need
a couple of stitches.

08:27.258 --> 08:29.510
Take her to Scarborough General,
okay?

08:29.593 --> 08:32.513
Daniel, can I see you
in my office please.

08:33.680 --> 08:35.348
You...

08:36.517 --> 08:38.352
...Aiden, right?

08:38.435 --> 08:39.770
Clean this up...

08:39.853 --> 08:42.523
...and when you're done,
just lock up, okay?

08:43.773 --> 08:45.358
Okay.

09:48.922 --> 09:51.008
Pardon me.

09:51.092 --> 09:52.008
Who are you?

09:52.092 --> 09:55.680
-Exactly?
-I'm Aiden.

09:55.763 --> 09:57.138
I'm an intern.

09:57.222 --> 09:59.142
Was that a question?

09:59.225 --> 10:01.352
MAGGIE:
How long have you been
an intern?

10:01.435 --> 10:03.020
Almost two months.

10:07.733 --> 10:09.402
You did that?

10:09.485 --> 10:11.237
Yeah...

10:11.320 --> 10:13.905
...Sorry, I shouldn't have
messed with your project.

10:13.990 --> 10:16.617
You changed the whole layout.

10:16.700 --> 10:18.868
Yeah, I--

10:18.952 --> 10:21.580
Rally sorry.

10:21.663 --> 10:24.958
I just thought
I'd try something.

10:34.635 --> 10:37.638
Do you think this colour
will suit Aiden?

10:38.805 --> 10:41.058
Yeah, it'll suit him well.

10:41.142 --> 10:43.977
You didn't even look.

10:44.062 --> 10:46.188
I don't have to look,
I can see it.

10:47.147 --> 10:48.815
Of course you can.

10:51.735 --> 10:53.653
It's Peter's favourite.

10:56.907 --> 10:58.825
Our Peter would have been
Aiden's age, now.

11:01.953 --> 11:05.165
He's a handsome young man.

11:05.248 --> 11:06.833
Mhmm.

11:06.917 --> 11:10.295
Sometimes, I think Aiden looks just like Peter.

11:18.137 --> 11:19.805
Celine...

11:22.392 --> 11:26.478
...you know Aiden is not Peter.

11:26.562 --> 11:28.980
Aiden can never become Peter.

11:51.087 --> 11:52.505
AIDEN:
Hey.

11:55.758 --> 11:57.468
I have some news for you.

11:59.428 --> 12:00.930
I'm waiting.

12:01.013 --> 12:04.350
Maggie wants to be your mentor.

12:04.433 --> 12:05.600
What?

12:05.683 --> 12:08.520
She sent in a request to HR.

12:08.603 --> 12:09.688
How do you know that?

12:09.772 --> 12:12.023
I know everything, remember?

12:18.238 --> 12:20.073
What are you doing here?

12:20.157 --> 12:21.658
Oh, nothing.

12:21.742 --> 12:22.618
Homework.

12:22.702 --> 12:25.203
Okay, put that away,
and look at this.

12:30.877 --> 12:32.210
Track suits?

12:32.293 --> 12:34.338
Velour track suits!

12:35.923 --> 12:36.965
It's so ridiculous!

12:37.048 --> 12:39.843
Who wears tracksuits outside
of the gym?

12:39.927 --> 12:41.470
Actually, people do.

12:41.553 --> 12:42.387
Oh really?

12:42.472 --> 12:44.973
Yeah, I see it all the time.

12:45.057 --> 12:48.185
I think Kanye wore one
to the Grammys one time.

12:48.268 --> 12:50.228
That was four years ago!

12:50.312 --> 12:52.482
In the fashion world,
it's like ancient!

12:52.565 --> 12:56.402
Yeah, but uh,
we could revive it, you know.

12:56.485 --> 12:59.028
Uh, keep this.

12:59.112 --> 13:00.948
Get rid of that...

13:01.032 --> 13:02.992
...and voilà!

13:03.075 --> 13:04.160
What?

13:04.243 --> 13:05.285
It'll work!

13:07.078 --> 13:08.997
I'm not sure.

13:09.080 --> 13:11.542
Anyway, put your thoughts
on paper and show me.

13:11.625 --> 13:12.877
Okay.

13:39.570 --> 13:41.197
-DANIEL: Hey.
-Hi.

13:43.615 --> 13:44.867
You know,...

13:46.910 --> 13:49.455
...tracksuits were my idea!

13:49.538 --> 13:52.123
They were my project.

13:52.207 --> 13:54.835
Michael just gave 'em to you?

13:54.918 --> 13:57.630
Yes, he did!

13:58.880 --> 13:59.757
MAGGIE:
Come in.

13:59.840 --> 14:01.092
-Hey.
-Hi Aiden.

14:01.175 --> 14:02.175
Come in.

14:02.258 --> 14:04.678
This is Aiden, my new intern.

14:04.762 --> 14:05.930
Hi.

14:09.350 --> 14:11.727
Daniel was just about to leave.

14:11.810 --> 14:13.395
Yeah.

14:13.478 --> 14:14.813
Good luck.

14:20.693 --> 14:22.655
What was that all about?

14:22.738 --> 14:25.407
It's fine, leave it.

14:25.490 --> 14:28.285
Anyways uh, take a look
at this proposal.

14:28.368 --> 14:30.870
There's some really good stuff
in here.

14:30.955 --> 14:34.750
Oh, and uh I was hoping we would
be done early today.

14:34.833 --> 14:37.377
Why? Have a date?

14:37.460 --> 14:39.713
No, uh,
just a friend and I.

14:39.797 --> 14:41.548
We're going to a bar,
to catch up.

14:41.632 --> 14:44.050
Oh well, I know a great bar!

14:44.133 --> 14:47.387
Good food, great drinks,
nice atmosphere.

14:47.470 --> 14:49.055
We uh...

14:49.138 --> 14:50.765
...go there a lot.

14:50.848 --> 14:52.768
-Oh, yeah?
-Oh, yeah.

14:55.020 --> 14:56.647
I think you've had enough
Daniel.

14:56.730 --> 14:58.023
You should go home.

15:00.692 --> 15:02.903
So, this is the watering hole?

15:02.987 --> 15:05.488
Yeah, I guess so.

15:05.572 --> 15:06.990
Nice.

15:08.617 --> 15:11.745
So, you know that girl
I was telling you about?

15:11.828 --> 15:14.582
The sexy girl
with the kinky boots?

15:14.665 --> 15:15.498
Who?

15:15.582 --> 15:16.833
The lingerie model?

15:16.917 --> 15:18.418
What are you talking about?

15:18.502 --> 15:19.878
I don't know any lingerie models

15:19.962 --> 15:22.463
or girls with kinky boots.

15:22.547 --> 15:23.757
Are you sure?

15:23.840 --> 15:24.883
You can tell me.

15:24.967 --> 15:26.552
I'll totally listen to all
your stories

15:26.635 --> 15:28.762
about the sexy sirens
you run into.

15:31.765 --> 15:33.433
Hi, how are you today?

15:33.517 --> 15:34.183
Uh, good.

15:34.267 --> 15:35.560
-How are you?
-Good!

15:35.643 --> 15:36.812
And what would you like?

15:36.895 --> 15:39.147
Our specials today are
the Von Sports-bar Burger

15:39.230 --> 15:40.898
or the Enforcer.

15:40.983 --> 15:42.483
-I'll do the Enforcer.
-Mhmm.

15:42.567 --> 15:43.985
And for you?

15:44.068 --> 15:46.197
Uh, beer is good.

15:46.280 --> 15:47.155
Just water.

15:47.238 --> 15:48.240
Alright, coming right up.

15:51.702 --> 15:54.788
I don't think you understand
what happens at our magazine.

15:54.872 --> 15:58.375
