walking around.

15:58.458 --> 15:59.502
No?

16:01.462 --> 16:03.380
At least, not until summer.

16:03.463 --> 16:05.923
Oh, when the swimsuit issue
comes out.

16:08.718 --> 16:10.220
Anyways....

16:10.303 --> 16:13.390
No, it's my mentor at work.

16:13.473 --> 16:15.100
Is she hot?

16:15.183 --> 16:17.268
Like you wouldn't believe!

16:17.352 --> 16:21.440
And she's smart
and sophisticated.

16:21.523 --> 16:22.983
Totally classy!

16:27.905 --> 16:32.075
Smart, sophisticated mentor.

16:32.158 --> 16:33.743
That's not what I pictured.

16:39.750 --> 16:42.293
Oh-- that's not her.

16:42.377 --> 16:43.795
That's Sophia.

16:43.878 --> 16:45.463
She's another one
of my colleagues.

16:45.547 --> 16:46.548
We hang out sometimes.

16:48.800 --> 16:51.970
Oh, I get it!
You got two birds in the net.

16:54.180 --> 16:56.517
No, it's not that.

16:58.268 --> 17:01.188
It's the guy
that she's talking to.

17:01.272 --> 17:03.107
What about him?

17:03.190 --> 17:04.858
He's an asshole!

17:04.942 --> 17:06.860
He’s always messing with Maggie.

17:10.447 --> 17:11.407
SELVA:
Maggie.

17:11.490 --> 17:12.950
Your mentor, the smart one?

17:13.033 --> 17:15.910
That's walking by us,
right now?

17:19.330 --> 17:21.375
DANIEL:
Hey, Maggie.

17:21.458 --> 17:22.250
Daniel?

17:22.333 --> 17:24.420
-I wanna talk to you.
-What about?

17:24.503 --> 17:26.130
-You're drunk.
-No, I'm not!

17:26.213 --> 17:27.047
We'll talk when you’re sober.

17:27.130 --> 17:28.048
What are talk--
no, no, no.

17:28.132 --> 17:28.965
You come back here.

17:29.048 --> 17:29.967
-Okay.
-Do not--

17:30.050 --> 17:31.385
Why don't you just go back
to Starbucks

17:31.468 --> 17:32.718
and have your face--

17:32.803 --> 17:33.428
Shit!

17:33.512 --> 17:34.597
Woah, woah, woah!

17:34.680 --> 17:35.972
What the fuck, man!

17:36.055 --> 17:36.890
Hey, Aiden, wait!

17:36.973 --> 17:38.225
Mind your fucking business.

17:38.308 --> 17:40.143
Get the fuck out,
you're dismissed!

17:40.227 --> 17:41.562
AIDEN:
You're at the bar,
you hit a girl!

17:41.645 --> 17:42.187
Fuck you!

18:03.208 --> 18:05.127
SELVA:
Well, that was interesting.

18:07.670 --> 18:09.840
Never been in a bar fight
before.

18:12.050 --> 18:15.303
Actually never even seen
a bar fight in my entire life.

18:35.740 --> 18:37.575
SELVA:
Black right?

18:37.658 --> 18:40.537
Yeah, thanks.

18:40.620 --> 18:43.207
No problem.

18:50.963 --> 18:55.135
Aiden, I know,
I'm not your father or anything.

18:58.138 --> 19:00.932
And I'm not trying to give you
a lecture

19:01.015 --> 19:05.062
