none of this looks good.

19:05.145 --> 19:07.563
You were there!

19:07.647 --> 19:08.732
You saw what happened!

19:08.815 --> 19:09.817
He pushed her!

19:09.900 --> 19:10.983
Hey!

19:11.067 --> 19:13.070
I was right there.

19:13.153 --> 19:14.237
I saw what he did.

19:15.655 --> 19:17.867
But I saw what you did.

19:17.950 --> 19:19.952
I didn't start it.

19:20.035 --> 19:22.537
SELVA:
Look man,

19:22.620 --> 19:24.413
I know you got
a thing for this girl.

19:24.497 --> 19:25.873
And I get that.

19:27.792 --> 19:31.045
But you're just started
in life.

19:31.128 --> 19:33.090
And all this fighting
and brawling,

19:33.173 --> 19:35.300
it's just gonna ruin it.

19:37.010 --> 19:38.137
Yeah.

19:42.015 --> 19:43.017
Yeah.

19:45.977 --> 19:47.353
I got that.

19:49.898 --> 19:50.565
AIDEN:
Hey.

19:50.648 --> 19:51.817
Hey.

19:51.900 --> 19:55.320
Oh, my God, that looks horrible.

19:55.403 --> 19:57.322
You should have taken a day off.

19:57.405 --> 19:58.657
I Couldn't.

19:58.740 --> 20:01.243
Gotta finish this project
for Maggie.

20:04.287 --> 20:05.872
Hello.

20:05.955 --> 20:08.458
Yeah, he's here.

20:08.542 --> 20:11.043
Okay, I'll let him know.

20:11.127 --> 20:12.462
Michael wants to see you.

20:12.545 --> 20:14.965
Me?
Was he mad?

20:15.048 --> 20:16.800
Sort of.

20:16.883 --> 20:18.385
Does he know about yesterday?

20:18.468 --> 20:20.803
I don’t know,
but I didn't tell him.

20:22.555 --> 20:23.723
