20:23.807 --> 20:26.602
I hope not,
but you better go now.

20:35.110 --> 20:37.612
Come on in.

20:37.695 --> 20:38.905
Have a seat.

20:45.453 --> 20:47.330
I'm not gonna ask you
why you and Daniel look like

20:47.413 --> 20:50.583
